! Concept Anchor Settlement State

A lineage tag preserving what an idea meant and whether it is `SEED`,
`FORMING`, `STABLE`, `CRYSTALLIZED`, or `COMPRESSED`.

!! Why It Matters

It keeps compressed research artifacts from losing their epistemic status.
That matters when half the stack is exploration and the other half wants proof.

